# SYSTEM 2: ANALYTICS STRATEGY SPECIFICATION
## UNJYNX Comprehensive Analytics & Metrics Framework

### 2.1 ANALYTICS ARCHITECTURE OVERVIEW

Three-layer analytics stack:
1. PostHog (Product Analytics) - User behavior, funnels, retention, feature flags, session replay
2. Prometheus + Grafana (Technical Metrics) - API performance, infrastructure health, queue monitoring
3. Sentry (Error Tracking) - Crash reporting, error grouping, release health, performance transactions

Data flow:
- Mobile app -> PostHog SDK (client-side events) + Sentry SDK (errors/crashes)
- Backend API -> PostHog Node SDK (server-side events) + Prometheus metrics endpoint + Sentry SDK
- BullMQ workers -> Prometheus metrics + custom PostHog events for delivery tracking
- All Prometheus metrics -> Grafana dashboards + Alertmanager -> Slack/Email/PagerDuty

### 2.2 BUSINESS METRICS

GROWTH METRICS:

| Metric          | Definition                                         | Target (Year 1)  | Benchmark                |
|-----------------|------------------------------------------------------|-------------------|--------------------------|
| Total Users     | All registered accounts                              | 50K               | -                        |
| DAU             | Unique users who open app in 24h                     | 5K                | -                        |
| WAU             | Unique users who open app in 7 days                  | 15K               | -                        |
| MAU             | Unique users who open app in 30 days                 | 25K               | -                        |
| DAU/MAU Ratio   | Stickiness indicator                                 | >20%              | 20% good, 25%+ excellent |
| DAU/WAU Ratio   | Weekly engagement depth                              | >40%              | 35%+ good                |
| Signup Rate     | New signups per day/week                             | 200/day by M12    | -                        |

RETENTION METRICS:

| Metric    | Definition                                | Target  | Industry Benchmark (Productivity) |
|-----------|--------------------------------------------|---------|-----------------------------------|
| D1        | % users active 1 day after signup          | >30%    | 17.1% average                     |
| D3        | % users active 3 days after signup         | >20%    | ~12% average                      |
| D7        | % users active 7 days after signup         | >15%    | ~8% average                       |
| D14       | % users active 14 days after signup        | >12%    | ~6% average                       |
| D30       | % users active 30 days after signup        | >8%     | 4.1% average                      |
| D90       | % users active 90 days after signup        | >5%     | ~2% average                       |

Note: UNJYNX targets 2x industry average due to multi-channel notification re-engagement advantage (WhatsApp/Telegram reminders pull users back).

REVENUE METRICS:

| Metric    | Definition                                           | Target (Year 1) |
|-----------|-------------------------------------------------------|------------------|
| MRR       | Monthly Recurring Revenue                             | $15K by M12      |
| ARR       | Annual Recurring Revenue (MRR x 12)                   | $180K by M12     |
| ARPU      | Average Revenue Per User (MRR / paying users)         | $5.50            |
| LTV       | Lifetime Value (ARPU x avg lifetime months)           | $66              |
| CAC       | Customer Acquisition Cost                             | <$10             |
| LTV:CAC   | Unit economics ratio                                  | >3:1             |
| Churn     | % paying users who cancel per month                   | <5%              |
| NRR       | Net Revenue Retention (expansion - contraction)       | >100%            |

CONVERSION METRICS:

| Funnel Step           | Definition                              | Target  | Benchmark           |
|-----------------------|------------------------------------------|---------|---------------------|
| Visitor -> Signup     | Landing page conversion                  | >8%     | 3-5% average SaaS   |
| Signup -> Onboarded   | Completed onboarding flow                | >60%    | 40-60% average      |
| Onboarded -> Activated| Reached "aha moment" (first task + reminder) | >40%    | 37.5% average       |
| Activated -> Retained | Active at D7                             | >50%    | 30-40%              |
| Free -> Trial         | Started free trial of Pro                | >15%    | 10-15%              |
| Trial -> Paid         | Converted trial to paid                  | >25%    | 15-25% opt-in       |

"Aha Moment" Definition for UNJYNX:
User has created at least 3 tasks AND received at least 1 external notification (WhatsApp/Telegram/SMS/Email) AND marked at least 1 task complete via notification action.

